With the announcement of the Victorious Graves chromas i imagine a lot more players will be trying to make a push towards gold in that queue type, or maybe they are just trying to reach gold in it or whatever their ranked goal is for the season. we only have twisted treeline ranked queues on Thursday nighttime and Friday nighttime, with one month left of the season that gives us about 8 nights left of twisted treeline queue, I just don&#039;t think this is enough time for people to reach their ranked goals. I urge to Riot give twisted treeline more server time towards the end of the season so that the players of that queue can make that final push they need! Otherwise I just don&#039;t think many people will be able to get that graves chroma or just the shiny boarder for that queue
